msgid "Optional token"
msgstr "Valfri token"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:664
msgid ""
"Modern book database with good coverage for newer books and series. Works"
" without a key, but an API token gives better rate limits."
msgstr ""
"Modern bokdatabas med bra täckning för nyare böcker och serier. Fungerar "
"utan nyckel men en API-token ger bättre rate limits."

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:668
msgid "API token (optional)"
msgstr "API-token (valfritt)"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:672
msgid "Leave empty for anonymous access"
msgstr "Lämna tomt för anonym åtkomst"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:679
msgid "Remove token"
msgstr "Ta bort token"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:680
msgid "Remove saved Hardcover token?"
msgstr "Ta bort sparad Hardcover-token?"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:689
msgid "How do I get a token?"
msgstr "Hur skaffar jag en token?"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:693
msgid "Create an account (free)"
msgstr "Skapa konto (gratis)"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:694
msgid "Copy your API token"
msgstr "Kopiera din API-token"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:696
msgid "Free beta — optional, works without a token."
msgstr "Gratis beta — valfritt, fungerar utan token."

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:698
msgid "Beta API — may change without notice. Token is valid for 1 year."
msgstr "Beta-API — kan ändras utan förvarning. Token gäller 1 år."

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:714
msgid ""
"Searches book covers via Wikidata and Wikimedia Commons. Best for "
"classics, well-known works and public domain books. Requires ISBN."
msgstr ""
"Söker bokomslag via Wikidata och Wikimedia Commons. Bäst för klassiker, "
"kända verk och public domain-böcker. Kräver ISBN."

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:728
msgid "DuckDuckGo image search"
msgstr "DuckDuckGo bildsökning"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:733
msgid ""
"Last fallback — searches for book covers via DuckDuckGo. Unofficial API "
"that may stop working. Good as a last resort for books not found in book "
"databases. Respects rate limiting."
msgstr ""
"Sista fallback — söker bokomslag via DuckDuckGo. Inofficiellt API som kan"
" sluta fungera. Bra som sista utväg för böcker som inte hittas i "
"bokdatabaser. Respekterar rate limiting."

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:744
msgid "Save settings"
msgstr "Spara inställningar"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:747
msgid "Test connections"
msgstr "Testa anslutningar"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:755
msgid "Connection tests"
msgstr "Anslutningstester"

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:763
msgid ""
"All keys are stored in a local database on your server. Alternatively "
"they can be set as environment variables — UI values take precedence."
msgstr ""
"Alla nycklar sparas i lokal databas på din server. Alternativt kan de "
"sättas som miljövariabler — UI-värden har prioritet."

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:770
msgid "Testing..."
msgstr "Testar..."

#: app/templates/settings_api.html:771
